    <title>使用Github Pages + Hexo搭建博客踩坑记录</title>
    <link href="https://constaniner.github.io/2021/03/31/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Github-Pages-Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/"/>
    <id>https://constaniner.github.io/2021/03/31/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Github-Pages-Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</id>
    <published>2021-03-31T01:46:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-03-31T13:40:22.597Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>使用Github Pages + Hexo搭建博客踩坑记录</h1><ol><li><p>Hexo d 无法部署到Github</p><p>检查站点配置文件（不是主题配置文件）的deploy部分</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repository:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:Username/Username.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使用的主题报错 / 预览跟Demo差很多 / 无法使用</p><p>建议新手使用诸如<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">Next</a>、<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">Fluid</a>等有较多人维护，仍然活跃的主题，这类主题通常有完善的配置引导供你入门。</p><p>如果看英文有困难的话，这里贴两个<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/3a05351a37dc?utm_campaign=maleskine&amp;utm_content=note&amp;utm_medium=seo_notes&amp;utm_source=recommendation">Next主题中文指引</a>、<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/getting-started.html">Next文档</a>，别的主题找找也会有类似的文章。</p></li><li><p>站点配置文件怎么写 / 各个关键字都是什么意思</p><p>请参考Hexo官方文档，写的很清楚<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">Hexo</a></p></li><li><p><code>Hexo g</code>报错<code>failed to detect version info, cannot read property 'replace' of undefined</code></p><p>大概率是Github连接问题。将你的梯子调整成全局 / pac模式能解决</p></li><li><p>Mac 用户安装 Node.js 报 EACESS 权限错误</p><p>请参考<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://docs.npmjs.com/resolving-eacces-permissions-errors-when-installing-packages-globally">npm官方文档</a>，强烈建议不要使用root覆盖安装</p></li><li><p>找不到好看的主题</p><p>这里推荐几个，主要是简约 / Material Design风格的</p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">Next</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">Fluid</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/Shen-Yu/hexo-theme-ayer">Ayer</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/bolnh/hexo-theme-material">Material</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://github.com/ppoffice/hexo-theme-icarus">ICARUS</a></p></li><li><p>找不到好看的icon</p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://fontawesome.com/">Font Awesome</a></p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
